Package fr.ensimag.ima.pseudocode

package fr.ensimag.ima.pseudocode
Implementation of the abstract data structure representing an IMA assembler program. A program is a list of Lines, each containing (possibly) a Label, an Instruction, and a comment (represented as a String).
Author:
Ensimag
